import React from 'react'; import { Button, ButtonToolbar, Card, CardBody, Col, } from 'reactstrap'; import { withTranslation } from 'react-i18next'; import PropTypes from 'prop-types'; const DefaultButtons = ({ t }) => (
{t('ui_elements.buttons.default_buttons')}
Use default button with necessary values of properties color, outline and disabled
